66
00:09:41,100 --> 00:09:42,940
Soon.

67
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:47,320
Ah. Don't mind me. I didn't ask because I was really curious.

68
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,530
I know.

69
00:09:49,430 --> 00:09:52,810
