72
00:09:58,350 --> 00:10:00,350
I just thought to myself though.

73
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:03,440
Maybe you thought aloud.

74
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,710
You could have chosen not to come.

75
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:08,820
There was no reason not to come.

76
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:18,130
