117
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:54,100
But I didn't see Eun Tak. She must be busy.

118
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,710
What is that?

119
00:12:57,310 --> 00:13:00,050
Me. It came out nicely.

120
00:13:04,610 --> 00:13:07,120
